Hello,

Sorry it is taking me so long to catch up. I have been sick this week.
Sore throat, Lost voice, generally achy and the lot of it all. I took
several days off from work as well. I am coming to the mending side of
things with judicious applications of NyQuil and Apple cider Vinegar,
honey and Cheyenne pepper

I hope to post soon. I generally don't have too much in the way of
creativity when sick :)

- Preston
